   <text><body>
         <div type="diary-day" xml:id="entry__1922-08-27">
            <p xml:space="preserve"><date when="1922-08-27">27/8</date> S.― Spazieren Böcklweiher ― <rs type="place" xml:id="pl_14202" ref="#place_f1dfd8c7fc6a5d35baf19f595d1b3571">Tristramweg</rs>.</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">Nm. Briefe (an <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_67080" ref="#person_13969"><roleName>Frau</roleName> <surname>Brevée</surname></rs>, <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_67081" ref="#person_16807"><forename>H.</forename> <surname>K.</surname></rs>); am <rs type="work" subtype="self" xml:id="bibl_2732">Verf.</rs> Wichtige Einfälle!―</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">Bahn. <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_67082" ref="#person_19832"><forename>O.</forename></rs> mit den <rs type="allusively" xml:id="rst_01924">Kindern</rs>, sowie <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_67083" ref="#person_18868"><surname>Pollaczeks</surname></rs> aus <rs type="place" xml:id="pl_14203" ref="#place_db263a77d65e66c98585e8f1a9ed7211">Lermoos</rs> ankommend; alle gesund 
und recht gut gestimmt. Gemeins. Nachtmahl im Hotel.―</p>
         </div>
